reviewText: This is an illegal release and a copyright infringement.

Yes, I downloaded it from internet for free. Ok, I am not sure if this flick considered mainstream  but nothing makes it great.
Story kinda invented to make room for two hot chicks but, of course, modesty prevail and we see nothing men wanna see.
I wonder when we learn all movies are illusion and, yes, Jess Franco looks better and better with every passing day.
Usually picture qualities of this kind of European films are poor, but this one is excellent.
Great talent in cast but this version had been edited and the cuts were jarring and poorly had been managed
